text: @pulte lost my job due to covid19, found out I won’t get a stimulus check bc I’m legally claimed as a dependent & parents only receive an additional $500 for children 16 &under. @ 20 years old I won’t receive any aid from the government & I still have to make car payment. $kylelin16
